Felipe Bacio Cortés, Lieutenant Colonel of the Mexican Air Force, and I say goodbye to all the honors that have come to him from Governor Jorge Torres López, the citizens and the state government, the Mexican Army through the Sixth Military District, the Mexican Air Force itself, the executives and students of the Saltillo High School of Technology, where he studied in 1985 and where he excelled in both study and sports.
